title: Sword Art Online: “If We Could Walk Together” - Novel Updates
author: Kawahara Reki   川原 礫
description: If We Could Walk Together is a continuation of If You Were Here and If You Wish It, an Alicization what-if storyline, answering the question of what would have happened if Raios and Humbert hadn't been around to force Eugeo and Kirito into breaking the Taboo Index.>
